## 1 Mathematical Framework  

### 1.1 Recursive Shell Geometry  
\[
R_n = R_0\,\phi^{\,n}, \qquad\kappa_n = \frac1{R_n}
\]

### 1.2 Scalar Field Equation  
\[
\nabla^{2}\Psi + k_n^{2}\,\Psi = 0, \qquad
k_n = \frac{2\pi}{R_0\,\phi^{\,n}}
\]

### 1.3 Energy Density  
\[
\mathcal{E}(r,t)=\tfrac12\bigl[\dot\Psi^2 + (\nabla\Psi)^2\bigr]\;\propto\;\phi^{-2n}
\]

